{
  "stem": "7437.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And what they did, they bartered on the outside, and they were able to obtain some paper, and some crayons, and some books.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we really looked forward to this school because it gave us something that a normal child would have.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And it took our thoughts away from the hunger, and from the drudgery, and hopelessness of it all.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But that school existed only for several months because pretty soon, they ran out of money to barter.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And also, there was such a hopelessness, and dismay, and chaos, and confusion.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And everybody became very much preoccupied with just trying to survive somehow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And so the school disappeared.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And now coming back to our so-called tunnel, we did go out-- and much to my mother's chagrin, even though I promised her I would not do it.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Because if one was caught outside of the ghetto, one paid with one's life.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But hunger is a very strong motivator.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we did go out and try to obtain some food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I remember one incident where I did get out and I sold a small ruby-- a gold and ruby ring for two eggs.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I was wearing a dress with puffed sleeves, and I put an egg in each puff.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And unfortunately, one of the Ukrainian guards caught me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And he found the eggs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "He threw the eggs on the sidewalk and made me kneel down and rub my face in the egg mixture, and screamed for me to get back where I belong and never to come out again outside.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "He was one of the kind-hearted ones.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
